import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import { Container } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Nav = () => {
  return (
      <Container>
        <Menu pointing secondary>
        <Menu.Item
          name='editorials'  
        >
          Editorials
        </Menu.Item>

        <Menu.Item
          name='reviews'        
        >
          Reviews
        </Menu.Item>

        <Menu.Item
          name='upcomingEvents'         
        >
          Upcoming Events
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Menu position='right'>
            <Menu.Item
              name='logout'
              active={activeItem === 'logout'}
              onClick={this.handleItemClick}
            />
          </Menu.Menu>
      </Menu>
      </Container>
  )
}

export default Nav
